# Train Ticket Application

This is a simple Spring Boot application of train ticket booking api service.

## Features

- Purchase train tickets.
- View ticket receipts.
- View users by section.
- Remove users.
- Modify user seats.

## Technologies Used

- Java
- Spring Boot
- Maven

## Setup Instructions

### Prerequisites

- Java 17 or higher
- Maven
- Git

### Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/NeerajY999/train-ticket-app.git
cd train-ticket-app
./mvnw spring-boot:run

